<br>
1. Am I correct on my belief that most cable internet providers frown on servers on their networks?<br>
<br>
2. If they do allow it, is it even slightly feasable if they don't assign a static IP? In Theory, your IP lease shouldn't expire if your machine is online most of the time.<br>
